			<div class="content" id="post-content-2241961">
									

<p>The true horror for me behind <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-209" target="_blank">The Sadist's Tumbler</a> isn't that it kills people, it's that it makes the predator comfortable to kill people.</p>
<p>But when do we feel like it's okay to torture and murder people?</p>
<p>Oh, there's a time. Perfectly natural. We all do it. And none of us mind at all.</p>
<p>It's when we dream.</p>

