<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>In this reimagining, <a href="/scp-209">SCP-209</a> is a device that can record and possibly create the dreams of its users. For whatever reason, a glass of scotch appears in each dream, and whoever drinks it gains control over the dream, as well as a hindered sense of empathy/care for others (although that may just be human nature.) The device can be used by two people at once, who will share the dream. However, if one of the users drinks the scotch and kills the other user, the user who was killed will cease to exist in the real world.</p>
</div>
